Feature: iframe Text Editor
    Scenario Outline: Delete, Format and Edit text in iframe text editor
        Given A iframe embedded text editor
        When A user do "<bold>", do "<italic>" and edit "<text>"
        Then The text is changed as per the user "<text>","<bold>" and "<italic>"

    Examples:
        | text | bold | italic |
        | hello | true | false |
        | How are you? | false | true |
        | Are u fine?| true | true |

scenario.name: Delete, Format and Edit text in iframe text editor

steps.text: A user do "<bold>", do "<italic>" and edit "<text>"
The text is changed as per the user "<text>","<bold>" and "<italic>"

pickle.name: Delete, Format and Edit text in iframe text editor

steps.text: A user do "true", do "false" and edit "hello"
The text is changed as per the user "hello","true" and "false"

pickle.name: Delete, Format and Edit text in iframe text editor

steps.text: A user do "false", do "true" and edit "How are you?"
The text is changed as per the user "How are you?","false" and "true"

pickle.name: Delete, Format and Edit text in iframe text editor

steps.text: A user do "true", do "true" and edit "Are u fine?"
The text is changed as per the user "Are u fine?","true" and "true"
